qualifiers.scope: Standard setbacks apply in most cases.
qualifiers.exclusions: Special setbacks override standard setbacks unless a larger contextual setback applies.

constants.specs: See zone for interior side setbacks for Flag lot and Substandard lot
constants.procedures: For front setback, if contextual setback is greater than 30' then it applies—otherwise, the 20' setback applies.

conditional_logic: If contextual setback is greater than 30', it applies
If both a contextual and special setback apply, the greater of the two setbacks is required

special_cases: Substandard corner lot < 50' wide has a street side setback of 10

logical_dependencies: Special setbacks override standard setbacks unless a larger contextual setback applies
